msgctxt "sn43.12:2.7"
msgid "Vipassanā. "
msgstr "Discernment. "

msgctxt "sn43.12:2.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo. "
msgstr "This is called the path that leads to the unconditioned. …” "

msgctxt "sn43.12:2.9"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ vo mayā asaṅkhataṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:2.10"
msgid "ayaṃ vo amhākaṃ anusāsanīti. (1.2) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.363, sc3
msgctxt "sn43.12:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr "“And what is the path that leads to the unconditioned? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.12:3.2"
msgid "Savitakko savicāro samādhi. "
msgstr "Immersion with placing the mind and keeping it connected. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:3.4"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:3.5"
msgid "Avitakko vicāramatto samādhi. "
msgstr "Immersion without placing the mind, but just keeping it connected. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:3.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:3.7"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:3.8"
msgid "Avitakko avicāro samādhi. Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe …. (1.3–5.) "
msgstr "Immersion without placing the mind or keeping it connected. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn43.12:4.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:4.2"
msgid "Suññato samādhi. "
msgstr "Emptiness immersion. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:4.4"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:4.5"
msgid "Animitto samādhi. "
msgstr "Signless immersion. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:4.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:4.7"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:4.8"
msgid "Appaṇihito samādhi. Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe …. (1.6–8.) "
msgstr "Undirected immersion. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.364, sc5
msgctxt "sn43.12:5.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.4"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vedanāsu vedanānupassī viharati … pe … "
msgstr "A mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.7"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.8"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu citte cittānupassī viharati … pe … "
msgstr "A mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the mind … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.9"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.10"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:5.11"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati … pe … ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe …. (1.9–12.) "
msgstr "A mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of principles … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.365, sc6
msgctxt "sn43.12:6.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. "
msgstr "A mendicant generates enthusiasm, tries, makes an effort, exerts the mind, and strives so that bad, unskillful qualities don’t arise. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.4"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. "
msgstr "A mendicant generates enthusiasm, tries, makes an effort, exerts the mind, and strives so that bad, unskillful qualities are given up. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.7"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.8"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. "
msgstr "A mendicant generates enthusiasm, tries, makes an effort, exerts the mind, and strives so that skillful qualities arise. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.10"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:6.11"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe …. (1.13–16.) "
msgstr "A mendicant generates enthusiasm, tries, makes an effort, exerts the mind, and strives so that skillful qualities that have arisen remain, are not lost, but increase, mature, and are fulfilled by development. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn43.12:7.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:7.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. "
msgstr "A mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm, and active effort. … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:7.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:7.4"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:7.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vīriyasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. "
msgstr "A mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy … "

msgctxt "sn43.12:7.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asaṅkhatagāmimaggo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn43.12:7.7"
